 I.  Gamma-Ray Production                                         9549 1451
    Gamma-ray production data from Howerton used in ENDF/B.VI.0   9549 1451
 was utilized for MT=3.  Isotropy in the center-of-mass system    9549 1451
 is assumed for all angular distributions.   Gamma-rays from      9549 1451
 radiative capture (MT=102) are given conventionally in files     9549 1451
 MF=12,14,15.  Semi-direct capture is included with the compound- 9549 1451
 nucleus contributions in both the gamma-ray production cross     9549 1451
 sections and in the gamma-ray emission spectra, which leads to   9549 1451
 an enhancement in the data for each at incident neutron and      9549 1451
 emission gamma-ray energies above about 10 MeV.                  9549 1451
